HEADWORD: Cornu Ammonis
<hw>Cor"nu Am*mo"nis</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧m*m⟦omac⟧"n⟦icr⟧s)</pr>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>\'d8Cornua Ammonis</plw></plu>. <ety>[L., horn of
Ammon. See <er>Ammonite</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A fossil
